          <article-title lang="original">메타 게임의 정체성 연구- 게임에 대한 게임을 중심으로 -</article-title>
          <article-title lang="foreign">Analysis of Identity of Meta Game - A Focus on Games about Games -</article-title>
          <article-title lang="english">Analysis of Identity of Meta Game - A Focus on Games about Games -</article-title>
        </title-group>
