          <article-title lang="original">게임 플레이 효과의 양면성과 게임 규제 태도 연구 :게임 장르를 중심으로</article-title>
          <article-title lang="foreign">Two Aspects of the Game Playing Effect and Attitude toward Game Regulation :Focused on Game Genre</article-title>
          <article-title lang="english">Two Aspects of the Game Playing Effect and Attitude toward Game Regulation :Focused on Game Genre</article-title>
