          <article-title lang="original">게임 산업을 통해 본 메타버스의 발전방안 - 게임과 게임형 메타버스 비교 중심으로 -</article-title>
          <article-title lang="foreign">Development Plan of Metaverse through Game Industry - Focusing on the Comparison between Games and Game-Based Metaverses -</article-title>
          <article-title lang="english">Development Plan of Metaverse through Game Industry - Focusing on the Comparison between Games and Game-Based Metaverses -</article-title>
