          <article-title lang="original">게임백서의 이용자 통계를 토대로 한 게임이용자 동향 및 게임시장의 성격 연구</article-title>
          <article-title lang="foreign">A Study on Game User Trend Based on User Statistics of Game White Paper and Characterization of Game Market</article-title>
