          <article-title lang="original">게임엔진을 활용한 게임 프로그래밍교육 시스템 개발 및 적용</article-title>
          <article-title lang="foreign">Development and Application of a Game Programming Education System Usiong Game Engine</article-title>
          <article-title lang="english">Development and Application of a Game Programming Education System Usiong Game Engine</article-title>
